00:03:25.270 --> 00:03:27.270
Jeremiah chapter one verse eight,

00:03:27.270 --> 00:03:34.270
where Jehovah told him to do not be afraid for I am with you to save you.

00:03:34.270 --> 00:03:39.270
Well, how that must have reassured Jeremiah because he continued in his ministry

00:03:39.270 --> 00:03:42.270
for some 67 years.

